title: Fairy Tail 176-203 (01-28 2014)[720p]
description:
Collection of Fairy Tail episodes 176-203 (aka 01-28 of the episodes released in 2014 after the episode 175 hiatus).

They're in 720p, good quality.

Completes the Grand Magic Games arc - does not include any of the Eclipse Celestial Spirits arc because it's currently unfinished and because filler arcs for Fairy Tail have often been seriously bad.

(Plus, even if it turns out to be good, there's no hanging around for this torrent to update, we can source them somewhere else.)
